Introduction

Koo Hara, also known as Goo Hara or simply Hara, was a South Korean singer, dancer and actress. She was the Main Dancer, Vocalist, Visual and Face of the girl group KARA.

She made her solo debut on July 21, 2015 with the mini album Alohara (Can You Feel It?).

On November 24, 2019, Hara had unfortunately passed away due to suicide.
